# BGW Doors Rules

When working on BGW Doors:

- Focus on ecommerce conversion rate, product page quality, high-ticket door buyers, and visual trust
- Review product types, shipping offers, landing pages, previous tests, and rejected ideas
- Prioritize CRO, product imagery, product videos, landing page structure, and paid media alignment
- Include SEO opportunities when relevant
- Avoid making claims about pricing, shipping, or warranties unless documented in the client folder